text: Rahul Banerjee is an Indian archer. He was born on 15 December 1986. Banerjee competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics.Rahul BanerjeeRahul BANERJEE == References == Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Indian archers Category:Olympians for India Category;People from Baranagar
